  "title": "Product Consultant",
  "description": "<p>· <strong>Customer Success: </strong>Develop and manage all client onboarding activities from project kick-off, training, configuration, data migration and “System Live”.</p>\n<p>· <strong>Project Management: </strong>Successfully and effectively manage implementation projects on schedule, and with high customer satisfaction; projects include implementation of different solutions including reservation, waitlist, &amp; table management; POS, Payment Gateway, Call Telephony Integration, Voice Booking System &amp; BI/Dashboard Reporting.</p>\n<p>· <strong>Account Management: </strong>Collaborate directly with restaurants &amp; hotels stakeholders to confirm goals, driving implementation of TableCheck at their venue and tailor configuration and communication toward those goals.</p>\n<p>· <strong>Product Guru : </strong>Be a product consultant, able to help clients learn the platform effectively and optimize their utilization based off their business requirement.</p>\n<p>· <strong>Team Player: </strong>Partner with Team Lead and Sales Representatives to support customers toward product adoption.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>· 1+ years of experience working in challenging, customer-facing roles, ideally within the SaaS industry or hospitality technology</p>\n<p>· Fresh Graduate Diploma or Degree in any field are welcome to apply.</p>\n<p>· Outstanding written and oral communication skills</p>\n<p>· Detail-oriented, strong critical thinking and problem-solving abilities</p>\n<p>· Love to connect with people, love foods, love to travel.</p>\n<p>· Positive &amp; keen to learn attitude.</p>\n<p>· Outstanding written and oral communication skills</p>\n<p>· Detail-oriented, strong critical thinking and problem-solving abilities</p>\n<p>· Love to connect with people, love foods, love to travel.</p>\n<p>· Fresh Graduate are welcome to apply.</p>\n<p>· Positive &amp; keen to learn attitude.</p>",
